      "title": "<span id=\"#14267\" class=\"scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold flex items-center\"><h1 class=\"inline !mb-1 scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold\">furnace</h1><div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(n.)</div></span>",
      "html": "<p>13世纪初，源自古法语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">fornais</i> “烤炉，熔炉”，比喻为“爱的火焰”（12世纪），来自拉丁语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">fornacem</i>（主格 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">fornax</i>）“烤炉，窑炉”，与 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">fornus</i>/<i class=\"foreign notranslate\">furnus</i> “烤炉”相关，与 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">formus</i> “温暖”相关，源自 PIE 词根 <a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of *gwher- \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/*gwher-\">*gwher-</a> “加热，温暖”。</p>"
    }
  ],
  "relate": [
    {
      "title": "*gwher-<div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\"></div>",
      "html": "<p>原始印欧语根，意为“加热，温暖”。</p><p>它构成或部分构成以下单词： <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of brand \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/brand\">brand</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of brandish \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/brandish\">brandish</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of brandy \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/brandy\">brandy</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of brimstone \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/brimstone\">brimstone</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of brindled \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/brindled\">brindled</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of forceps \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/forceps\">forceps</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of Fornax \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/Fornax\">Fornax</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of fornicate \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/fornicate\">fornicate</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of fornication \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/fornication\">fornication</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of fornix \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/fornix\">fornix</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of furnace \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/furnace\">furnace</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of hypothermia \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/hypothermia\">hypothermia</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of thermal \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/thermal\">thermal</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of thermo- \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/thermo-\">thermo-</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of Thermopylae \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/Thermopylae\">Thermopylae</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of Thermos \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/Thermos\">Thermos</a>。</p><p>它是一个假设的词源，其存在的证据由以下单词提供： <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">gharmah</i>（梵语）“热”； <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">Garmapada-</i>（古波斯语），第四个月的名称，对应于六月/七月，来自 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">garma-</i> “热”； <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">war-</i>（赫梯语）“燃烧”； <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">jerm</i>（亚美尼亚语）“温暖”； <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">thermos</i>（希腊语）“温暖”； <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">formus</i>（拉丁语）“温暖”， <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">fornax</i> “烤炉”； <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">fogeir</i>（古爱尔兰语）“加热”； <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">bærnan</i>（古英语）“点燃”。</p>"
